snippet.title: King's Quest Chapter 3: Once Upon A Climb Launch Trailer
snippet.description: In his latest adventure, King Graham recounts his most personal tale yet. When the magic mirror reveals the location of his one-true love, Graham must climb to daring new heights to save his future Queen. But what he encounters there might just send his notions of romance sailing out the window.
